headline: ONEOK to Sell Three Interstate Natural Gas Pipeline Systems for $1.2B
summary: OKE is set to sell its three interstate natural gas pipeline systems. This deal will align and enhance its capital allocation priorities within its integrated operating footprint.

headline: 2 Durable Dividend Stocks That Have Delivered Decades of Stability and Growth
summary: The dot.com crash, financial crisis, and pandemic have severely affected many companies, forcing several to cut their dividends due to falling profits.  Enbridge (NYSE: ENB) and Oneok (NYSE: OKE) are two of those stalwarts.  Enbridge is a remarkably consistent company.
